Description: bc-* ecosystem application runtime (development files)
 Application-lifecycle runtime: init/run/cleanup flow, layered
 configuration, structured logging, metrics (counter / gauge /
 histogram), and a CLI framework for argv parsing and subcommand
 dispatch.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-runtime.
